-- Bed Bath & Beyond posts higher quarterly profit
-- 
-- Wed Jun 27, 2007 4:24pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/06/27/us-bedbathbeyond-results-idUSWEN903420070627

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Home furnishings retailer Bed Bath & Beyond Inc. ( BBBY.O ) posted a higher quarterly profit on Wednesday as sales rose. 

 The company said first-quarter net income rose to about $104.6 million, or 38 cents a share, from $100.4 million, or 35 cents a year earlier.